      <!-- ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ -->
      <t id="50">Currently, there are no available stations where we could restock our desired equipment.</t>
      <t id="51">Currently, all available stations lack the required resources to manufacture the necessary equipment.\nI will go to the nearest station, place a request for restocking, and then await the next resource replenishment.</t>
      <t id="52">We lack the necessary funds to restock the desired equipment.</t>
      <t id="53">The process of creating the restock order has failed.</t>
      <t id="54">The restock equipment order has failed. More detail is available in the logbook.</t>
